課程教材 Course Material
	    Lecture notes    

參考書目 References
	    Do Carmo, Differential Forms
Griffiths and Harris, principal of algebraic geometry
Hartshorne, algebraic geometry,
Kodaira, complex manifolds    

備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
        無    

核心能力 Competence
□ 掌握連續與逼進的能力
 Ability to handle continuity phenomena and approximations.
□ 處理數字及符號運算的能力
 Ability to operate with symbols and digits.
□ 透視形像與空間的能力
 Ability to visualize space, shape, and images.
□ 利用計算機處理數學的能力
 Ability of computer to do mathematics.
□ 應用隨機理論的能力
 Ability to apply stochastic mathematics.
□ 處理大量數據的能力
 Ability to handle large amount of data.
□ 處理離散型數學的能力
 Ability to do mathematics relating to discrete models.
■ 獨立研究與撰寫論文的能力
 Ability to do independent researches and to write thesis.
□ 使用計算機的能力
 Abilities to use computer as a tool.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       每週對於所指導之研究生所課程安排之討論課程。Will arrange a discussion per week for students.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    學習基本的幾何與拓樸學不變量的概念    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Differential forms2de Rham cohomology3Integration on Manifolds4Complex manifold5Complex Varieties6Homology7Cohomology8Vector bundles9Connections, Curvature10Sheaves11Cech Cohomology12de Rham theorem13Dolbeault theorem14Sobolev spaces15Hodge decomposition16Kodaira-Serre Duality17Kahler manifolds18final week 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


